Change_YoY_1.query:
q = load "${App.Datasets.daily_temperature_year.FullyQualifiedName}";
q = filter q by 'Year_Number' <= {{cell(Year_2.selection, 0, "avg_Year_Number").asString()}};
result = group q by 'Year';
result = foreach result generate q.'Year' as 'Year', avg(q.'{{cell(display_selector_1.selection, 0, "Measure3__field").asString()}}') as 'A';
result = group result by 'Year';
result = foreach result generate 'Year', first(A) as 'A', sum(A) - sum(sum(A)) over ([-1..-1] partition by all order by ('Year')) as 'B';
result = order result by ('Year' asc);
result = limit result 2000;

Max_over_time_1.query:
